ata/Epic/EpicGamesLauncher/VaultCache/FabLibrary/PILLOWS_PACK-146ed13a/fbx/fbx_extracted/__MACOSX/FBX/._SM_Pillow_5.fbx","name":"","material_index":-1,"lods":[]},{"file":"C:/ProgramData/Epic/EpicGamesLauncher/VaultCache/FabLibrary/PILLOWS_PACK-146ed13a/fbx/fbx_extracted/__MACOSX/FBX/._SM_Pillow_6.fbx","name":"","material_index":-1,"lods":[]}],"materials":[],"native_files":[],"additional_textures":[],"metadata":{"launcher":{"version":"0.0.1","listening_port":24563},"fab":{"assetNamespace":"","listing":{"averageRating":5,"createdAt":"","description":"<p>Add realism to your projects with this set of high-quality 3D pillows!</p><p></p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li><p><span><strong>Variety of Shapes:</strong> Includes <strong>6 unique meshes</strong> (models) of various shapes and styles</span></p></li><li><p><span><strong>Two Material Types:</strong> Comes with colorful and grey-basic colorways</span></p></li><li><p><span><strong>Color Customization:</strong> The grey and white material is designed for easy repainting, </span><span class=\"fabkit-prose-color--yellow\"><strong>but you can only change the color and texture in third-party software</strong> (e.g., Substance Painter or Photoshop)</span></p></li><li><p><span><strong>All models are optimized for efficient use in game engines and rendering</strong></span></p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Ideal For:</strong></p><ul><li><p><span>Architectural Visualization (ArchViz)</span></p></li><li><p><span>Populating Game Scenes (Props)</span></p></li><li><p><span>3D Advertising Projects</span></p></li></ul><p><strong>Universal 3D Pillow Pack (6 Meshes, 2 Materials)</strong></p><p>Add realism to your projects with this set of high-quality 3D pillows. Ideal for <strong>architectural visualization (ArchViz)</strong> and interior decoration in game engines <strong>(Unreal Engine, Unity)</strong>.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p><span><strong>Variety of Shapes:</strong> Includes <strong>6 unique meshes</strong> (models) of various shapes and styles (square, rectangular, round, and decorative).</span></p></li><li><p><span><strong>Two Material Types:</strong> Comes with basic materials, including realistic <strong>leather imitation</strong>and fabric options.</span></p></li><li><p><span><strong>Color Customization:</strong> The grey and white material is designed for easy repainting, <strong>but you can only change the color and texture in third-party software</strong> (e.g., Substance Painter or Photoshop).</span></p></li><li><p><span><strong>Optimization:</strong> All models are optimized for efficient use in game engines and rendering.</span></p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Ideal For:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li><p><span>Architectural Visualization (ArchViz)</span></p></li><li><p><span>Populating Game Scenes (Props)</span></p></li><li><p><span>3D Advertising Projects</span></p><p></p></li></ul><p>Bring comfort and style to your digital world today!</p>","isAiForbidden":true,"isAiGenerated":false,"lastUpdatedAt":"","listingType":"3d-model","media":"https://media.fab.com/image_previews/gallery_images/50544e13-d757-4bc5-a1ea-9733ba469abf/42aa0ebd-4e09-4d90-83ab-43f15f61f546.png","publishedAt":"2025-12-04T10:27:53.490856Z","reviewCount":1,"thumbnail":"https://media.fab.com/image_previews/gallery_images/6570cbe6-c7af-4e7f-aeca-3351aaed06c3/c70abdb9-c5f4-4d0c-b148-4b47c8d04e56.png","title":"PILLOWS PACK","uid":"146ed13a-c714-4f87-9078-a2710837a1f5","updatedAt":"","user":{"coverImageUrl":"https://cdn1.epicgames.com/fab/seller/o-68y9zn2rmqjrr8hp36xuqxvlhnygtk/cover/8a1f4ede.png","profileImageUrl":"https://cdn1.epicgames.com/fab/seller/o-68y9zn2rmqjrr8hp36xuqxvlhnygtk/profileImage/blob-500x500-4f0cd373ba93dcd3d2b5d0f7985a56a3.jpg","sellerName":"Kurmanin Tailor","uid":"e914c491-d100-4eb0-ba79-9334843ec798"},"tags":[{"name":"Retro","slug":"retro","uid":"01b64ec5-7261-4c99-a280-a34680f1af03"},{"name":"Pbr","slug":"pbr","uid":"080edd3b-d10a-4f32-ace2-30f5baa480dc"},